						               													<description>ALP is a game that is creepy enough to be seriously fun where you get to hunt ghosts with friends. And the ghosts get to hunt you back.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Tired of babyish ghost games for scaredy cats, but not about to bust out the ouija, because you know better? Ready for a real ghost themed board game to shiver your timbers while you battle your friends?  This one's real... Real fun.  Up to 6 players can play as skeptics OR believers. Compete to collect evidence cards and survive ghosts effects from each haunted location you dare to investigate. But beware, when you play with ghosts, they play back.  Will you be the Psychic, the TV host, The Camera Guy, The Agent, The Priest or the Skeptic? And will you beat the bumps in the night? Roll the dice, spin the ghost effects planchette. Be the first to prove or debunk, while sabotaging your meddling colleagues. Don't get labeled a quack and hold on to your evidence! The hunt is on.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
